{"tid":949080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京認同美國從敘利亞撤軍　英法德質疑特朗普決定","createTime":"2018-12-20T14:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T20:50:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec9124c5dc0652a33905c5d78c60366994ea93d","tid":949080,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1434344_1_L_20181220211125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1434344_1_L_20181220211125.jpg&h=4fc78407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普京歡迎特朗普從敘利亞撤軍的決定。（美聯社）<br />\n美國總統特朗普宣布美軍由敘利亞撤兵，特朗普之後在社交網站表示，美國不想當中東警察，反問美國沒有獲得什麼，但以失去寶貴的生命和數以萬億美元，保護那些在幾乎所有情況下都不欣賞美國正在做事的人。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京歡迎美國的決定，但英法德都提出質疑。<br />\n<br />\n普京說，認同特朗普指在敘利亞戰勝「伊斯蘭國」，但恐怖份子有流向鄰近地區的風險，俄羅斯會繼續留守敘利亞。<br />\n<br />\n德國外長發表聲明指，美國撤兵可能危及與伊斯蘭國武裝分子的戰鬥，以及在前線取得的成果。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相文翠珊發言人表示，仍會致力在敘利亞打擊「伊斯蘭國」武裝份子，重申各國聯合打擊行動取得巨大成果，但仍然需要做得更多。<br />\n<br />\n法國亦表示將繼續參與打擊「伊斯蘭國」的聯合行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434344-20181220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434344-20181220.htm&d=qOnrDpP%2BJXSbynmDzAHLI9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8b4319ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434344-20181220.htm&h=4a16f35e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434344-20181220.htm</a>"},{"pid":"300e2e71182def6984b5927a9d70494e7eba7972","tid":949080,"uid":158613,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"歐洲軍隊 到你哋接力啦"},{"pid":"5ac104d007e1f2e812b0d9b2d96839ea93fc6ea1","tid":949080,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"America First!"},{"pid":"3ffdb68c90c2747a74572956583affab4176c37d","tid":949080,"uid":76216,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0